    <name>Alper Han</name>
  </developer>
  <summary>Mouse and keyboard macro automation tool for X11</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      CrossMacro is a powerful mouse and keyboard macro recording and playback tool.
      This Flatpak version supports X11 sessions only. Wayland is not supported due to protocol restrictions.
      Please use an X11 session to run this application.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Record and replay mouse movements, clicks, and keyboard events</li>
      <li>Text Expansion support for productivity</li>
      <li>Global hotkeys for control</li>
      <li>Adjustable playback speed and loop mode</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.alper_han.crossmacro.desktop</launchable>
